Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    The Player can be represented as a circle with position and velocity vectors. In Player's act method, collision detection is ran with an ArrayList of all obstacles present in the current level, which is given by the Game class.
    Author:
    Edward
